---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "../components/CTAButton.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="CBT — TT Motorcycle School"
  description="Compulsory Basic Training (CBT) in Sussex with TT Motorcycle School. One day course, DVSA approved, all bikes provided. Book your CBT online."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">Compulsory Basic Training</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title">CBT — Your First Step on Two Wheels</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__sub">
        Your CBT certificate is the legal requirement to ride on UK roads. TT
        Motorcycle School delivers professional, friendly CBT training across
        Sussex.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-grid">
      <div class="prose">
        <h2>What is the CBT?</h2>
        <p>
          The Compulsory Basic Training (CBT) is a one-day course that every new
          rider must complete before riding a moped or motorcycle on public
          roads in the UK. Once complete, you receive a DL196 certificate, valid
          for 2 years.
        </p>

        <h2>Where Do I Start?</h2>
        <p>
          At TT Motorcycle School we make the CBT a positive, enjoyable
          experience. You don't need any prior experience just a positive
          attitude and a willingness to learn.
        </p>

        <p>
          Included in the course price is: motorcycle or scooter hire,
          motorcycle safety clothing and a helmet.
        </p>

        <h2>What to Expect</h2>
        <p>Your CBT day covers five elements:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <strong>Introduction and eyesight check</strong> — a safety briefing and
            paperwork
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Practical on-site training</strong> — learning to control the
            bike in a safe, off-road environment
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Essential riding skills</strong> — braking, steering, gear changes
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>On-road training</strong> — riding on public roads with your instructor
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Certificate of completion</strong> — your DL196 certificate, valid
            for 2 years
          </li>
        </ol>

        <h2>What You'll Need</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>A valid UK driving licence or provisional licence</li>
          <li>
            To be at least 16 years old (mopeds) or 17 years old (motorcycles)
          </li>
          <li>
            Appropriate clothing — <a href="/what-to-wear/">see our guide</a>
          </li>
          <li>Glasses or contact lenses if required</li>
          <li>
            Able to ride a bicycle competently with good control and balance
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What Comes Next?</h2>
        <p>
          After your CBT, you can ride solo on a restricted machine. From there,
          many riders go on to their <a href="/full-licence/"
            >full motorcycle licence</a
          >. We'll guide you through every step of that journey too.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar__card">
          <h3 class="sidebar__title">Book Your CBT</h3>
          <p class="sidebar__body">
            Secure your place online. Spaces fill up quickly.
          </p>
          <CTAButton
            href="/cbtbooking/"
            label="Book Now"
            variant="accent"
            size="md"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar__card sidebar__card--plain">
          <h3 class="sidebar__title">Quick Info</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar__info-list">
            <li><strong>Duration:</strong> Full day (approx. 6–8 hrs)</li>
            <li><strong>Minimum age:</strong> 16 (moped) / 17 (motorcycle)</li>
            <li><strong>Certificate valid:</strong> 2 years</li>
            <li><strong>Bikes provided:</strong> Yes</li>
            <li><strong>Location:</strong> Sussex</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/prices/" class="sidebar__price-link">View CBT Price →</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-10);
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    }
  }

  .sidebar__card {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .sidebar__card--plain {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .sidebar__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .sidebar__body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: #ccc;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .sidebar__info-list {
    list-style: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-normal);
  }

  .sidebar__info-list strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .sidebar__price-link {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    transition: color var(--transition);
  }

  .sidebar__price-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .prose a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
